<pre><code class='hljs language-mdx'><span class='hljs-quote'>> 不要透過共享記憶體來通信，而是透過通信來共享記憶體。</span>
<span class='hljs-quote'>>
> — <span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>cite</span>></span></span>羅布·派克[^1]<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>cite</span>></span></span></span>
