</section><section class='heading' data-heading-rank='2'><h2>其它 — abbr、sub、sup、kbd、mark、del</h2>
<pre><code class='hljs language-mdx'><span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>abbr</span> <span class='hljs-attr'>title</span>=<span class='hljs-string'>'圖形交換格式'</span>></span></span>GIF<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>abbr</span>></span></span> 是一種點陣圖影像格式。

H<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>sub</span>></span></span>2<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>sub</span>></span></span>O X<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span>n<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span> + Y<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span>n<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span> = Z<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span>n<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>sup</span>></span></span>

按 <span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span>CTRL<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span> + <span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span>ALT<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span> + <span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span>Delete<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>kbd</span>></span></span> 結束會話。

大多數<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;<span class='hljs-name'>mark</span>></span></span>蠑螈<span class='xml'><span class='hljs-tag'>&#x3C;/<span class='hljs-name'>mark</span>></span></span>都是夜間活動的，捕食昆蟲、蠕蟲和其他小生物。

~~刪除線~~
</code></pre>
<p><abbr title='圖形交換格式'>GIF</abbr> 是一種點陣圖影像格式。</p>
<p>H<sub>2</sub>O X<sup>n</sup> + Y<sup>n</sup> = Z<sup>n</sup></p>
<p>按 <kbd>CTRL</kbd> + <kbd>ALT</kbd> + <kbd>Delete</kbd> 結束會話。</p>
<p>大多數<mark>蠑螈</mark>都是夜間活動的，捕食昆蟲、蠕蟲和其他小生物。</p>
